RUN: @mhost_bin -s 8.8.8.8 --no-system-lookups --ascii --no-color discover example.com -p -s --no-ct-logs

CHECK: > Options: mode=multi, concurrent nameservers=10, max. nameservers=100, concurrent requests=5, retries=0, timeout=5s, ndots=1, abort on error, abort on timeout
CHECK-NEXT: > Requesting all record types.
CHECK-NEXT: - Sending
CHECK-NEXT: - Received
CHECK-NEXT: * SOA:
CHECK-NEXT: * NS:
CHECK-NEXT: * NS:
CHECK-NEXT: * MX:
CHECK-NEXT: * TXT:
CHECK: * TXT:
CHECK: * A:
CHECK: * AAAA:
CHECK: > Skipping CT logs (disabled).
CHECK: > TXT record mining.
CHECK: > SRV service probing.
CHECK: > Checking wildcard resolution.
CHECK-NEXT: - Sending
CHECK-NEXT: - Received
CHECK: > Attempting zone transfer (AXFR).
CHECK: > Attempting NSEC walking.
CHECK: > Wordlist lookups.
CHECK-NEXT: - Sending
CHECK-NEXT: - Received
CHECK: > Subdomain permutation lookups.
CHECK: > Reverse DNS lookups.
CHECK: + Finished.
CHECK-NEXT: - Received
CHECK-NEXT: - No wildcard resolution discovered
CHECK: * .example.com.
